data: {"type":"content_block_delta","index":1,"delta":{"type":"text_delta","text":" C++, making it ideal for performance-critical applications. Games, operating systems, browsers, and embedded systems benefit"}}

event: content_block_delta
data: {"type":"content_block_delta","index":1,"delta":{"type":"text_delta","text":" from Rust's low-level control while maintaining the productivity benefits of higher-level languages.\n\n## Key Features\n\nRust offers several powerful features:\n\n- **Pattern Matching**: Express"}}

event: content_block_delta
data: {"type":"content_block_delta","index":1,"delta":{"type":"text_delta","text":"ive matching against data structures\n- **Traits**: A powerful system for defining shared behavior\n- **Zero-C"}}

event: content_block_delta
data: {"type":"content_block_delta","index":1,"delta":{"type":"text_delta","text":"ost Abstractions**: High-level features that don't sacrifice performance\n- **Concurrency**: Safe multi-threaded programming without data races\n\n## Growing"}}

event: content_block_delta
data: {"type":"content_block_delta","index":1,"delta":{"type":"text_delta","text":" Ecosystem\n\nThe Rust ecosystem has matured significantly. Cargo, its package manager and build tool, makes dependency"}}

